<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_799dcb3ee449.aspx"><b>国风·卫风·伯兮</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a></p>
<div class="contson" id="contson799dcb3ee449">
伯兮朅兮，邦之桀兮。伯也执殳，为王前驱。<br />自伯之东，首如飞蓬。岂无膏沐？谁适为容！<br />其雨其雨，杲杲出日。愿言思伯，甘心首疾。<br />焉得谖草？言树之背。愿言思伯。使我心痗。
</div>
</div>
